"This example produces a MANIFEST.MF that contains [package version identification] for the package common."

"package version identification" links to http://download-llnw.oracle.com/javase/1.5.0/docs/guide/versioning/, which is non-functional.

http://docs.oracle.com/javase/1.5.0/docs/guide/versioning/spec/versioning2.html#wp89936 might be a better link, or http://docs.oracle.com/javase/1.5.0/docs/guide/versioning/.
creator: jacob@broadinstitute.org
